      <title>Gemini 将向客户返还 11 亿美元，并在监管和解中支付罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/gemini-return-11-bln-customers-pay-fine-settlement-with-new-york-regulator-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[监管机构周三表示，作为与纽约金融服务部 (NYDFS) 达成和解的一部分，加密货币交易所 Gemini 将向其已失效贷款计划的客户返还至少 11 亿美元，并因不安全和不健全的行为支付 3700 万美元的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/gemini-return-11-bln-customers-pay-fine-settlement-with-new-york-regulator-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMC 因好莱坞上映推迟而遭受的损失超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/theater-chain-amc-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[连锁影院 AMC Entertainment 周三公布季度亏损超出预期，原因是泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 和碧昂斯 (Beyonce) 演唱会电影的发行成本上升，以及好莱坞电影公司在遭遇两次罢工后缺乏大片上映。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/theater-chain-amc-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:23:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
